snippet.title: THE Vampire Diaries Video
snippet.description:
If the cast of Vampire Diaries see this please let them know I’m single, unless it’s Jeremy tell him I found peace

S01E13 “The 14th Party of the Season” https://www.patreon.com/JennyNicholson
S06E05 “[Song Title]” https://twitter.com/JennyENicholson
S04E22 “The Mummy vs. Frankenstein” https://www.twitch.tv/progamerjenny
Seasons 1-4 & Seasons 7-8 https://www.instagram.com/spider_jewel/
S03E19 “Vampire Fight!” https://spiderjewel.tumblr.com/
S08E01 “A clipshow of all the adventures Bonnie had every time she was offscreen for the past 8 seasons” https://www.facebook.com/JennyNicholsonVids/
